TI  - H-GIS and Digital Strategies for the Documentation and Preservation of the Serenissima's Cultural Heritage: Spatio-Temporal Mapping of Itineraries along the Adriatic Coast
PY  - 2025
T2  - International Archives of the Photogrammetry, Remote Sensing and Spatial Information Sciences - ISPRS Archives
